headline: Intuit to Host Annual Investor Day on September 18
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., September 04, 2025--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, will host its annual Investor Day at its headquarters in Mountain View, CA on September 18, 2025 at 8:00 a.m. Pacific Time.
